snippet: The fiancée of Oregon Governor John Kitzhaber said on Thursday she had once married a 18-year-old immigrant student in exchange for some $5,000 she used to pay her school tuition and buy a laptop....

headline.print_headline: Oregon Governor's Fiancée Admits to Illegally Marrying Immigrant
headline.main: Oregon Governor's Fiancée Admits to Illegally Marrying Immigrant

lead_paragraph: The fiancée of Oregon Governor John Kitzhaber said on Thursday she had once married a 18-year-old immigrant student in exchange for some $5,000 she used to pay her school tuition and buy a laptop.
